# Stage-gate satisfier for containerized field services (BIC-meta#336 stage model).
# INTENTIONALLY EMPTY of values: all real config is injected via each service's
# docker-compose.yml `environment:` block from the host-level field .env — the
# launch environment always wins over this file (pydantic-settings precedence).
# It exists only so the services' no-default APP_ENV gate (app/core/stage.py)
# finds its .env.prod in the container WORKDIR (/app).
